name: Ashley Schultz
description:
Ashley Schultz is an American pop singer and social media personality.

1000-step TI trained on a dataset of 20 images with my usual settings.

I had attempted to train a TI based on Ashley a few times before, but failed quite badly. That was some weeks ago and I think upscaling her pics had a very negative effect on the final results. Since then, I've altered my process a bit, and I think this time around the results are good enough to be published. She's not exactly the most famous of the girls I've uploaded so far, but I've always liked her looks a lot and I think she deserves a decent embedding. Hope you'll like it! :)

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)
